		voertuignr = MAGIC,
		kenteken = REGNO,

	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: false,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: false) ~> SelectColumnsFromVehiclerecords
VehiclerecordsAutolineLst30dgn filter(STATUS == 'C') ~> FilterVehiclerecords
SelectColumnsFromVehiclerecords, RdwData join(kenteken_ == RdwData@Kenteken,
	joinType:'left',
	matchType:'exact',
	ignoreSpaces: false,
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinRdwData
JoinRdwData derive(Bekend_bij_rdw = case(isNull(RdwData@Kenteken), false(), true())) ~> AddColumnBekendBijRdw
FilterVehiclerecords derive(dms = {_SET},
		kenteken_ = trim(replace(REGNO, '-', '')),
		prospectnummer = case(DRVMAGIC != 0, DRVMAGIC, case(AFTMAGIC != 0, AFTMAGIC, SALMAGIC)),
		bedrijfsnummer = case(COMMAGIC003 != 0, COMMAGIC003, case(COMMAGIC002 != 0, COMMAGIC002, COMMAGIC001)),
		datum_deel1_dms = REGDATE,
		datum_deel2_dms = DELDATE,
		apk_datum_dms = MOTDATE,
		garantie_datum = WAREXPDT,
		next_service = NEXTSERV,
		laatste_bezoek = LASTWORK,
		laatste_service = case(year(LASTSERV)>= 1753, LASTSERV),
		bedrijf = coalesce(right(LOCN001, 2),right(AFTLOCN, 2)),
		edited = case(isNull(EDITED),case(isNull(CREATED),addDays(currentDate(), -365) , CREATED) , EDITED)) ~> AddColumns
AddColumnBekendBijRdw filter(isNull(voertuignr) == false()) ~> FilterVoertuigen
VehiclerecordsIdas, VehiclerecordsIdasCarvarB join(left(BCHAVA, 3) == CVMDEL
	&& BMODYR == CVMOJJ
	&& BPRCDE == CVPRCD,
	joinType:'left',
	matchType:'exact',
	ignoreSpaces: false,
	broadcast: 'auto')~> LeftJoinCarvarB
LeftJoinCarvarB, VehiclerecordsIdasCarvarC join(substring(BCHAVA, 4, 2) == right( toString(CVENGT),2)
	&& BMODYR == VehiclerecordsIdasCarvarC@CVMOJJ
	&& BPRCDE == VehiclerecordsIdasCarvarC@CVPRCD,
	joinType:'left',
	matchType:'exact',
	ignoreSpaces: false,
	broadcast: 'auto')~> LeftJoinCarvarC
LeftJoinCarvarC, VehiclerecordsIdasCarvarE join(substring(BCHAVA, 6, 2) == right( toString(CVVRSE),2)
	&& BMODYR == VehiclerecordsIdasCarvarE@CVMOJJ
	&& BPRCDE == VehiclerecordsIdasCarvarE@CVPRCD,

	matchType:'exact',
	ignoreSpaces: false,
